transcripts: The Ashley Restaurant Quality Tablecloth by Wamsutta was designed exclusively for Bed Bath and Beyond. This beautiful leaf branch tablecloth is made from 100% cotton. The pattern offers a casual elegance making it a perfect choice for occasional or formal entertaining, napkin sets are also available in the same pattern. The Ashley Restaurant Quality Tablecloth by Wamsutta is available exclusively online and at select Bed Bath and Beyond stores.
